Description_lang: Hurls a Phoenix that deals $257542s2 Fire damage to the target and reduced damage to other nearby enemies.$?a343222[Always deals a critical strike.][]

description_blz.en_US: Hurls a Phoenix that deals 4,671 Fire damage to the target and reduced damage to other nearby enemies.

description_blz.de_DE: Schleudert einen Phönix, der dem Ziel 4.820 Feuerschaden und anderen Gegnern in der Nähe verringerten Schaden zufügt.

description_blz.ko_KR: 불사조를 날려 대상에게 4,783의 화염 피해를 입히고 주위의 다른 적에게 감소된 화염 피해를 입힙니다.
